                            img.imgshow(src='https://www.vietnamairlines.com/~/media/Images/Discovery/Vietnam/QUYNHON/canh%20dep/1920x1080/Quynhon_canhdep_dam_thi_nai_1920x1080.jpg', style='width:100%;height:100%; padding-right:4px;border-radius:5px')
                            .imgtext(style='color:white') Đầm Thị Nại
                    .column1
